This file explains the sequence for running the case

a) Execute localy the "RunLocal1" script

b) Send to the cluster the following file.
    -jobScript_shm
    
c) After the meshing is done, execute localy the "RunLocal2" script.

d) Send to the cluster the following file.
    -jobScript_rm
    
e) After finishing, send to the cluster the following file.    
    -jobScript_pf
    
----------------------------------------WARNING! THIS STEP TAKES ~28h----------------------------------------
f) After finishing, send to the cluster the following file.    
    -jobScript_sf    
----------------------------------------WARNING! THIS STEP TAKES ~28h----------------------------------------

g) After the end of the run (check if folder "5000" exists in Group6_Case/processor* folders) execute the following command:
    -reconstructPar
